      "commented_at": "2026-07-08T07:56:18Z",
      "verb": "commented",
      "text": "This is put perfectly. And the flip side helps too: the ability to accept people's functions and dysfunctions, that they make mistakes and don't always give you what you want right away, is exactly what will help the people now trying to manage AI.",
