      "verb": "commented",
      "text": "𝥽𝧮𝧹𝧸: https://github.com/ondatra-ai/true-bdd \nFair warning: it's a prototype, not a polished tool. Behavioural spec + architecture management is real; full regeneration isn't there yet. Feedback from people building in this space is what I'm after.",
